{"TopicId":199206,"ForumId":104,"TopicTitle":"ModuleLight - help needed- referencing multiple meshes in config","CreatedByName":"L0ck0n","CreatedById":179874,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T19:07:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"L0ck0n","CreatedById":179874,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T19:07:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to reference multiple light sources in config file or to add mulitple lights to one object? Sth like:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0MODULE\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0{\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0name = ModuleLight\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0lightName = \u003Cstrong\u003Elight1 , light2\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0useAnimationDim = True\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0lightBrightenSpeed = 2.5\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0lightDimSpeed = 2.5\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0resourceAmount = 0.03\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0animationName = lights\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0useResources = True\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0}\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JPLRepo","CreatedById":114736,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T22:12:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot exactly like that.\u003Cbr\u003E\nBut you can add multiple \u0022ModuleLight\u0022\u00A0 MODULE instances to your part.cfg.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"L0ck0n","CreatedById":179874,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T22:32:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223901483\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022199206\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609366340\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022114736\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JPLRepo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, JPLRepo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot exactly like that.\u003Cbr\u003E\nBut you can add multiple \u0022ModuleLight\u0022\u00A0 MODULE instances to your part.cfg.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThx, also one more thing, is there some way to change light color in config file, in\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003EModuleLight?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JPLRepo","CreatedById":114736,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T22:36:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223901500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022199206\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609367535\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179874\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022L0ck0n\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, L0ck0n said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThx, also one more thing, is there some way to change light color in config file, in\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003EModuleLight?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou sure can. Set the \u0022lightR\u0022 \u0022lightG\u0022 \u0022lightB\u0022 variables to normalized RGB (float)values in the cfg.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"L0ck0n","CreatedById":179874,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T22:38:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223901504\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022199206\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609367800\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022114736\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JPLRepo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, JPLRepo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou sure can. Set the \u0022lightR\u0022 \u0022lightG\u0022 \u0022lightB\u0022 variables to normalized RGB (float)values in the cfg.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThx, could u post here example how it should look like?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JPLRepo","CreatedById":114736,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T22:40:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223901505\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022199206\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609367896\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179874\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022L0ck0n\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, L0ck0n said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThx, could u post here example how it should look like?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-c prettyprinted\u0022 id=\u0022ips_uid_4779_20\u0022 style=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EMODULE    \n\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E{\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n  name \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022typ\u0022\u003EModuleLight\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n    lightName \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E light1\n    useAnimationDim \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022typ\u0022\u003ETrue\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n    lightBrightenSpeed \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022lit\u0022\u003E2.5\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n    lightDimSpeed \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022lit\u0022\u003E2.5\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n    resourceAmount \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022lit\u0022\u003E0.03\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n    animationName \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E lights\n    useResources \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E=\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022typ\u0022\u003ETrue\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E\n    lightR \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u002