0n said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry, , but for me its not working xD.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTested on stock parts too, light color is not changing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou seem to have found a bug it would appear.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"L0ck0n","CreatedById":179874,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-30T23:22:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223901528\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022199206\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221609370370\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022114736\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JPLRepo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, JPLRepo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou seem to have found a bug it would appear.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep, xD.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso on stock landing gear there is problem with light texture, its always enabled, even if landing gear is folded , i found that just now xD.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}